  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior/Staff Nurse",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Providing quality care</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work with Senior/Nurse Manager to analyse and evaluate nursing care plan provided for the residents.</li>\n  <li>Co-ordinate with Enrolled Nurses to implement care plan such as medication, hygiene care, social and physical activities for the residents.</li>\n  <li>Identify symptoms of residents that are related to illnesses and/or decline in functional and cognitive abilities and advocate early medical attention.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Training &amp; Development</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Mentor and guide Enrolled Nurses, Nursing Aides/ Assistants and Healthcare Assistants in performing their functional duties.</li>\n  <li>Participate in relevant quality improvement and assessment activities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Administration and management</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Educate family members of residents on the residents’ health conditions and help them gain understanding on the holistic care provided.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all documentation of residents’ case is maintained appropriately.</li>\n  <li>Deputise Senior/Nurse Manger in his/her absence</li>\n  <li>Any other duty as assigned by the Director of Nursing or Senior/Nurse Manager</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/Diploma in Nursing from an recognised institution as approved by Singapore Nursing Board</li>\n  <li>Nurses with post basic/advance diploma in Mental Health or those with previous experience in psychiatric setting are welcome to apply.</li>\n  <li>Demonstrate good communications and people engagement skills, preferably the use of local languages and dialects.</li>\n  <li>Good organisation ability Able to form networks and strong linkages with stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Able to work shifts</li>\n  <li>Candidates with the relevant nursing qualification without experience will be considered.</li>\n  <li>For Senior position, at least 7 to 8 years of experience, preferably with experience in public healthcare or nursing home sector.</li>\n  <li>Various locations available: Bukit Batok, Senja, Woodlands, Tampines, Pearl's Hill</li>\n</ul>",
